    "These models also made use of language characteristics.",
    "The development of mathematical models reached its peak in the 1980s and 1990s.",
    "These models may calculate the probability of word sequences in a given context using probabilistic modeling approaches [57].",
    "Even though ML algorithms have proven to be capable of effectively analyzing large datasets, there have been challenges in interpreting language, particularly contextual and semantic components [58].The area of language modeling has grown significantly since the introduction of LLMs in the middle of the 2010s.",
    "The algorithms used deep learning techniques to evaluate vast amounts of textual data to identify structures and patterns in language usage [59]."
